{"build_type":"library","description":"Bounded busy-read of the first 8-byte slot of a shared memory region until it becomes non-zero, returning the observed value (or zero if the attempt budget is exhausted). This is the explicit STAND-IN for the still-open cross-thread wake (worker-runtime-FINAL A4): a parent reading a result a spawned worker wrote into a per-instance shared region. No global, no eventfd, no futex. Tail-recursive with top-level recursion and early-return guards to stay within the compiler's safe shape.","module_name":"poll-region-slot-until-nonzero","package_name":"poll-region-slot-until-nonzero","function_definitions":{"poll-region-slot-until-nonzero":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"region","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"tries","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"eight","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":8},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"dbaddr","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"alu_operation","operator":"+","target":"dbaddr","lhs":{"value":"region"},"rhs":{"value":"eight"}},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"suspend-caller-awaiting-doorbell-readiness","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"dbaddr"},{"kind":"var","value":"zero"}],"result_assignment_variable":"m","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"array_read","dest":"v","base":"region","index":"zero","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"v"}}]}}}